text:
URL `GET /api/project`

Get information about a specific project.

Request
```javascript
{
    "token": "CB23C3395153D2414CE7FF22F925776DBF72BF309",      /* Login token */
    "project": "time rest"  /* Name of the project where you want to get info */
}
```
Response success
```javascript
{
    "success": true,        /* If the action was successful */
    /* Project object */
    "project": {
         name: "TestAPI", /* Project name */
         owner: "yogsther", /* Username of the owner */
         /*All members, including the owner and how much work they have done*/
         members: [
              {
                   username: "yogsther",
                   name: "Olle K.", /* Members full name*/
                   work: 1999900 /* Work committed in ms*/
              }
         ]
    }
}
```
Response failure
```javascript
{
    "success": false,
    "reason": "Invalid token, invalid project"
}
